SUMMARY:
DELIVERY OPTIONS: Home delivery (PPL, Česká pošta) and parcel shop/pickup point delivery (Zásilkovna, PPL, Česká pošta) are available. 
PRICING: Standard delivery costs range from 79 Kč to 119 Kč. Free shipping is offered on all orders over 2 500 Kč. 
NOTABLE FEATURES: A flat COD surcharge of 49 Kč applies to all cash on delivery orders. Česká pošta guarantees delivery by the next working day after dispatch. No express or weekend delivery options are mentioned. 
WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is well-structured and easy to find on a dedicated page. The use of tables clearly outlines costs based on order value. However, it lacks delivery time details for PPL and Zásilkovna and does not explicitly mention services like parcel lockers.
